---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import AboutHero from "../components/AboutHero.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Navbar />
  <main class="flex-grow">
    <AboutHero />

    <!-- Our Mission Section -->
    <section class="bg-surface-container py-24">
      <div
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center"
      >
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-primary/5 p-4 inline-block rounded-2xl">
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl"
              style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
            >
              health_and_safety
            </span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">
            She has lived firsthand the same challenges she is trying to help
            solve...
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-body leading-relaxed">
              Romina is passionate about connecting families with resources that
              make their lives better. Her family encountered similar challenges
              moving to a new place with limited language skills. Originally
              from Honduras and growing up in the City of Boston she overcame
              many challenges. This has been the deeper driver of her behavior.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-body leading-relaxed">
              Starting her career in retail developing and executing national
              marketing strategies for Fortune 500 companies supporting brands
              like Marshalls/TJMaxx and Staples, Inc. Romina found her calling
              for promoting products and services to improve people’s lives and
              wellbeing.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-body leading-relaxed">
              That was the moment when she transitioned into community health
              care. By combining her vast experience in marketing, branding, and
              business development with community health and wellness initiative
              that engage diverse and vulnerable communities, she developed a
              methodology for immediate impact for all organizations involved in
              the healthcare process.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Romina’s proprietary strategy has been used to strengthen referral
              programs, local branding, and social media presence that promote
              specifically to ethnically diverse and hard-to-reach audiences.
              Through producing and hosting her own TV Shows to promote local
              health awareness campaigns, Romina has built a brand that can be
              leveraged for the good of the community overall, as well as
              developed the expertise in video production which has been found
              to increasingly enhance communication to bilingual healthcare
              consumers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div
            class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 space-y-4 transform translate-y-12"
          >
            <span class="text-5xl font-headline font-black text-secondary/30"
              >98%</span
            >
            <p class="font-label text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase">
              Stakeholder Trust
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-primary text-white p-8 rounded-2xl space-y-4">
            <span class="text-5xl font-headline font-black opacity-40">15+</span
            >
            <p class="font-label text-sm font-bold uppercase">
              Cities Transformed
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-200 p-8 rounded-2xl space-y-4 col-span-2">
            <p class="font-body text-lg italic text-slate-700">
              "Ready to expand your possibilities of what you can accomplish? Contact Romina Wilmot below for a meet & greet at your workplace or somewhere in the community."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 20+ Years of Impact (Timeline) -->
    <section class="py-24">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-8"
        >
          <div>
            <span
              class="font-label font-bold text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-4 block"
              >Our Evolution</span
            >
            <h2 class="font-headline text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900">
              20+ Years of <span class="text-secondary">Impact</span>
            </h2>
          </div>
          <p class="max-w-md text-slate-600 mb-2">
            A timeline of systemic change and unwavering commitment to public
            health excellence.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
          <div
            class="group relative pt-12 border-t-2 border-slate-200 hover:border-primary transition-colors duration-500"
          >
            <span
              class="absolute top-0 -translate-y-1/2 left-0 font-headline text-6xl font-black text-slate-200 group-hover:text-primary/20 transition-colors"
              >01</span
            >
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">
              Foundational Leadership
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Pioneering community-based health initiatives and establishing the
              first empathy-led clinical protocols in metropolitan hospitals.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="group relative pt-12 border-t-2 border-slate-200 hover:border-primary transition-colors duration-500"
          >
            <span
              class="absolute top-0 -translate-y-1/2 left-0 font-headline text-6xl font-black text-slate-200 group-hover:text-primary/20 transition-colors"
              >02</span
            >
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">
              System Integration
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Developing cross-sector partnerships that linked social services
              directly with primary healthcare for a holistic approach to
              wellness.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="group relative pt-12 border-t-2 border-slate-200 hover:border-primary transition-colors duration-500"
          >
            <span
              class="absolute top-0 -translate-y-1/2 left-0 font-headline text-6xl font-black text-slate-200 group-hover:text-primary/20 transition-colors"
              >03</span
            >
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">
              RW Consulting Birth
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              The formal establishment of our consultancy, scaling these proven
              methodologies to global policy makers and NGOs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Core Values Section -->
    <section class="bg-primary text-white py-24">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-20">
          <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Core Values</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 opacity-80">
            The principles that guide every strategy we build and every
            relationship we nurture.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div
            class="p-10 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl hover:bg-secondary transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col items-center text-center group"
          >
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary group-hover:text-white mb-6"
              >verified_user</span
            >
            <h4 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold mb-3">Integrity</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 group-hover:text-white/90">
              Unwavering ethical standards in every policy recommendation.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="p-10 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl hover:bg-secondary transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col items-center text-center group"
          >
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary group-hover:text-white mb-6"
              >favorite</span
            >
            <h4 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold mb-3">Empatía</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 group-hover:text-white/90">
              Centering human experience in institutional frameworks.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="p-10 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl hover:bg-secondary transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col items-center text-center group"
          >
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary group-hover:text-white mb-6"
              >lightbulb</span
            >
            <h4 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold mb-3">Innovación</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 group-hover:text-white/90">
              Creative solutions for complex healthcare challenges.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="p-10 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl hover:bg-secondary transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col items-center text-center group"
          >
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary group-hover:text-white mb-6"
              >handshake</span
            >
            <h4 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold mb-3">Colaboración</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 group-hover:text-white/90">
              Building bridges across public and private sectors.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
        <div
          class="bg-surface-container p-16 rounded-[2.5rem] relative overflow-hidden shadow-xl"
        >
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-10">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[120px]"
              >architecture</span
            >
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-8">
            Let's Build Together
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto">
            Ready to transform your vision into systemic change? Let's design a
            future that works for everyone.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
            <button
              class="bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:brightness-110 transition-all shadow-lg active:scale-[0.98]"
            >
              Schedule Consultation
            </button>
            <button
              class="bg-secondary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-all shadow-lg active:scale-[0.98]"
            >
              Explore Services
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3/4 h-64 bg-primary/5 blur-[120px] -z-0"
      >
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
